description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, dynamic and motivated qualified registered nurse and ODP to join our friendly Orthopaedic Theatre Scrub team here at Mid Essex Hospital Trust, Chelmsford, working at Broomfield and Braintree Community Hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a busy and exciting department consisting of 23 operating theatres and the specialties covered are Robotic Surgery, Vascular – endovascular (Hybrid theatre), Urology, Upper GI, Colorectal, Emergency, ENT, Gynaecology, Head and Neck, General, Orthopaedics, Burns and Plastics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome both experience and non-experience staff to join our supportive team. Full training will be provided in an encouraging learning environment which includes preceptorship, supernumerary status while achieving competencies, an in-house courses, support for revalidation and leadership development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to work across all specialties once competent is required. As we are a large department our staff have the opportunity to work in day/night rotation, bank holidays and weekend.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
